                            <comment id="16630260" author="lapo@lapo.it" created="Thu, 27 Sep 2018 11:40:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Today I have had even an 11 columns result: &lt;tt&gt;1010.18 KiB&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16655302" author="cnlwsu" created="Thu, 18 Oct 2018 14:23:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The offset should be from the max width instead of hard coded since it can vary so much. The other nodetool outputs have been moving to use&#160;&lt;tt&gt;TableBuilder&lt;/tt&gt; so that it always aligns properly. Perhaps this table can be changed to use it as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16886529" author="kirktrue" created="Tue, 16 Jul 2019 22:47:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Using&#160;&lt;tt&gt;TableBuilder&lt;/tt&gt; in latest patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
